node.text:
Search Winnebago Weekly on YouTube! New channel, new people, new content, even a new host! Completely different show than Rodeo Time. Different camera man, director and editor. 

Meet the whole @rodeo.time team in this show: @jorden395 @williewardle @kait_coward @kevin_reed_ @blytheepp @leroy_gibbons @abrilsimental @twobargabe @nemyp_ @megnnrae @donnie.daytona also Lisa, David, and Neely!
